{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 94853, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啊，越来越高级看不懂了", "timestamp": 1594045556, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 94856, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "高中美术课上讲过，怀念美术老师", "timestamp": 1594045595, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 94865, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啊，经常见到的一张图", "timestamp": 1594045689, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 94869, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有没有带艺术家来赏析一下~", "timestamp": 1594045704, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 94883, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这种真的看不懂有什么技术上或者是内涵上的意义了，谁给讲讲？", "timestamp": 1594045789, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 94894, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 这种作品细节就比较重要了，光看这种网络图片看不出来。你可以去找找高清的版本，放大了看看细节。（我的理解）", "timestamp": 1594045889, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 94911, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "蒙德里安是风格画派，新造型主义的代表人物。作品大多运用最基本的元素（三原色、矩形、黑色的不同粗细的线条）来表现不同事物的张力，并在其中找到和谐的平衡。", "timestamp": 1594046098, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 94914, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "纯粹而抽象的形式能够更接近神性或者哲学吧", "timestamp": 1594046111, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 94993, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "个人觉得想要理解现代艺术中抽象的意义的话，可以把这一时代的作品联系起来，比如绘画和建筑，像是蒙德里安的风格主义运动和柯布西耶的现代主义建筑在精神上就有很强的相似性；或者是绘画和家居设计，里特维尔德的红蓝椅就是极受蒙德里安作品影响的设计。它们都在追求极致的理性、形式感、象征性。", "timestamp": 1594046637, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 95017, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 15885, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "当然大家也可以去了解一下时代背景~当时排斥装饰的倾向和抽象几何的机器美学都和工业化发展有一定联系~(我应该没说错8要是有误大家别打我555)", "timestamp": 1594046857, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 623, "w": 500}, "likenum": 7, "pid": 15885, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "皮特·蒙德里安《Composition with Blue and Red》", "timestamp": 1594045488, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1606782588, "url": "6c/6cnlk53oskl3vndc5a7mkjeu3rh6nwlo.jpeg", "vote": {}}}